title: Meditrade Nitrile® 3000 White Examination Glove - Powder & Latex Free Disposable Exam Gloves - Suitable for Multiple Sectors - Size Medium - 100pcs
features: MULTIPURPOSE: Can be used for a range of purposes, such as medical examinations, surgical operations, professional cleaning and using disinfectants, in factories and laboratories, pharmaceutics, handling food, hairdressing, and in the beauty sector. These gloves will keep you safe and clean for all your needs.

TEAR RESISTANT: Elastic and tear-resistant, with an ambidextrous fit for both men and women. Their rolled edge also makes them easy to put on while adding strength. Can also be double gloved for situations where you want additional security.

SKIN FRIENDLY: Powder-free for extra versatility, and micro-roughened for a comfortable and secure grip that lets you confidently hold any tool. Protein-free and latex-free, making them ideal for people with sensitive skin and allergies.

CERTIFIED: Non-sterile examination gloves safe on skin according to DIN EN 455, are safe for single use, and prevent cross contamination of fluids and chemicals. Suitable for handling cleaning products, in the pharmaceutical industry, catering and food handling in general.

PROTECTION AT ALL TIMES: At Meditrade, we are constantly building on and expanding our expert knowledge to develop innovative protective clothing that protects you at all times, so you can work safely and confidently
description: From the manufacturer Multipurpose ✓ Our gloves offer excellent protection for environments with a high risk of contamination. ✓ Can be safely and confidently worn for surgery, examinations, working in factories, handling chemicals, catering, using cleaning and disinfectant products. Withstands Any Environment ✓ Ambidextrous gloves are designed with a rolled edge so they are easily donned for a secure fit. ✓ Tested according to EN 455. Committed to Innovation ✓ At Meditrade, we believe in having “Passion in Health”. With our expert knowledge, we’re constantly developing innovative products that you can rely on for strength, protection, and comfort in any industry.
